Standing in the little park, I turn my eyes to the ancient fountain.

<<if $Read gte 1>>//I wonder if I can use what I've learned from that old book to decipher some of the engravings?//  I think of the old leather bound tome I had found beneath the church.

<</if>><<if ($PlayerOccult + $PlayerIntelligence) gte 15 && $Read gte 1>>My years of studying every strange thing I could find, combined with the little bit of time I have spent reading the old tome, it only takes me a couple of minutes before I start to recognize patterns and similarities among the runes on the ancient fountain that I have also seen in the book.  Making sense of it all eludes me however.

//There just isn't enough here to properly start to translate it.  Maybe I can ask around and see if I can learn anything useful from the locals?  The General Store might be a good place to start.//

<<set $FountainInvestigated to "Played">>
<<elseif ($PlayerOccult + $PlayerIntelligence) gte 12 && $Read gte 3>>My passing familiarity with strange things like this, combined with the time I have spent reading the old tome, I'm able to recognize several of the runes on the ancient fountain that I have also seen in the book.  It takes me quite a bit of time before I realize I'm out of my depth on this problem, at least until I can learn more.

//There just isn't enough here to properly start to translate it.  Maybe I can ask around and see if I can learn anything useful from the locals?  Nadia might be a good place to start.//

<<set $FountainInvestigated to "Played">>
<<elseif ($PlayerOccult + $PlayerIntelligence) gte 9 && $Read gte 5>>After all the time I have spent reading through the old tome, I start to look at the fountain, my eyes drifting slowly over the strange symbols chiseled in its ancient surface.  I see a few symbols here and there that I recognize from my time reading the book, but nowhere near enough to start making sense of it all.

